, H., Deforestation and degradation of peatlands (2007) Peatlands International, 2, pp. 32-34; Ritung, W.S., Subagjo, H., (2003) Maps of Area of Peatland Distribution and Carbon Content in Sumatera 1990-2002, , Bogor, Indonesia: Wetlands International\Indonesia Programme & Wildlife Habitat Canada (WHC); Suparto Ritung, W.S., Subagjo, H., (2004) Map of Peatland Distribution Area and Carbon Content in Kalimantan 2000-2002, , Bogor, Indonesia: Wetlands International\Indonesia Programme & Wildlife Habitat Canada (WHC); Wösten, J.H.M., Berg Den J.Van, Van Eijk, P., Gevers, G.J.M., Giesen, W.B.J.T., Hooijer, A., Idris, A., Wibisono, I.T., Interrelationships between hydrology and ecology in fire degraded tropical peat swamp forests (2006) Water Resources Development, 22, pp. 157-174","Miettinen, J.; Centre for Remote Imaging, Sensing and Processing, National University of Singapore, Blk SOC-1 Level 2, Lower Kent Ridge Road, Singapore 119260, Singapore; email: crsjim@nus.edu.sg",,,,,,,,00447447,,AMBOC,21053723,"English","Ambio",Article,Scopus,2-s2.0-84755161318
